blockquote.pre:
auto cs = get_completion_signatures<child-type<Sndr>, FWD-ENV-T(Env)...>();
auto fn = []<class... Ts>(set_value_t(*)(Ts...)) {
  if constexpr (!invocable<remove_cvref_t<data-type<Sndr>>, Ts...>)
    throw unspecified-exception();
};
cs.for-each(overload-set{fn, [](auto){}});

discussion.p:
The line auto fn = []<class... Ts>(set_value_t(*)(Ts...)) { 
is correct when then-cpo is `then` but not when it is `upon_error` or `upon_stopped`.


For `upon_error` it should be:

blockquote.pre:
auto cs = get_completion_signatures<child-type<Sndr>, FWD-ENV-T(Env)...>();
auto fn = []<class... Ts>(set_value_tdecayed-typeof<set-cpo>(*)(Ts...)) {
  if constexpr (!invocable<remove_cvref_t<data-type<Sndr>>, Ts...>)
    throw unspecified-exception();
};
cs.for-each(overload-set{fn, [](auto){}});
